description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;University College London Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust (UCLH) where outstanding care and clinical excellence come together every day.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a Registered Mental Health Nurse looking for a part time or full time position ?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So why join UCLH…?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;• We have a reputation as a centre of clinical excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;• Our hospitals are in great central London locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;• We have new facilities and state-of-the-art medical technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;• We have a wide range of career opportunities that we can offer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Nurses are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work across all UCLH departments gaining invaluable skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to “Lines of Work” (guaranteed short, medium or long term shifts)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated recruitment team to ensure you can work as quickly as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bookings team to ensure you work when and wherever you want to&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free mandatory training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, we are looking for Nurses that can offer us:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for delivering excellent patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to learn new skills as we can offer training in some departments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to communicate effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 Months recent NHS experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested and have the correct experience for the role please do apply online today.&lt;/p&gt;
